    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">
        E-sika Knowledge Base & Guides
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-indigo-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Everything you need to know to get the most out of your E-sika store
