                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Configure your store's basic settings to create a strong foundation:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                      <li>Choose a unique subdomain for your store (e.g., yourstore.e-sika.com)</li>
                      <li>Connect a custom domain if you have one</li>
                      <li>Configure your general store settings (currency, timezone, etc.)</li>
                      <li>Set up tax settings based on your business requirements</li>
                      <li>Configure shipping settings (if selling physical products)</li>
                      <li>Set up payment gateways to start accepting payments</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x400?text=Store+Settings+Screenshot" alt="Store Settings Screenshot" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow">
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                  <button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 text-left font-medium text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50" 
                          data-action="accordion#toggle" 
                          aria-expanded="false"
                          data-accordion-target="trigger">
