                      <li>Customize colors, fonts, and layout</li>
                      <li>Upload your logo and favicon</li>
                      <li>Set up your homepage including featured products, collections, and promotional banners</li>
                      <li>Create navigation menus</li>
                      <li>Add custom pages (About Us, Contact, etc.)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
