                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                      <li>Navigate to Products > Add New</li>
                      <li>Choose the product type (physical, digital, or service)</li>
                      <li>Enter product details (name, description, price)</li>
                      <li>Upload product images</li>
                      <li>Configure product options and variants (if applicable)</li>
                      <li>Set inventory levels (for physical products)</li>
                      <li>Configure shipping settings (for physical products)</li>
                      <li>Add SEO information to improve discoverability</li>
